data.description: Welcome to this stunning, newly renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home ideally located in the desirable neighborhood of North Walpole. This charming residence offers a perfect blend of modern updates and classic appeal.  The renovated kitchen boasts butcher-block countertops, contemporary cabinetry, and beautiful stainless steel appliances. The adjacent pantry area offers ample additional storage with its beautiful original built-in cabinetry.   The remainder of the first floor offers a large open-concept space including dining, living, and an office space / bonus room. The three bedrooms and a half bath upstairs provide comfort and convenience. Both bathrooms have been tastefully updated with modern fixtures and finishes.  Situated just 30 minutes from Keene, this home offers a perfect balance between tranquility and accessibility. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to Route 91, which is only 5 minutes away.  Outside, you’ll find a spacious backyard, perfect for hosting outdoor gatherings or enjoying peaceful moments in the fresh air. The oversized detached garage provides convenient parking and loads of extra storage space.  All major systems are new including plumbing feeds and drains, electric, heat/AC, water heater, roof (including garage), siding, and windows.  Don’t miss the opportunity to make this beautifully renovated home in North Walpole your own.  Open houses scheduled for 7/8/23 and 7/9/23 10am-noon and 1pm-3pm.
